	(bbdb-pgp): Rename from bbdb/pgp-sign.  Make it a command.
	Consider all message recipients in bbdb-pgp-headers.  Use
	bbdb-pgp-ranked-actions, bbdb-pgp-headers, and
	bbdb-pgp-method-alist.
