	bbdb-new-mails-always-primary.
	(bbdb-add-name, bbdb-add-aka, bbdb-add-mails)
	(bbdb-new-mails-primary): Unify set of allowed values.
	(bbdb-add-job, bbdb-eval-spec): New functions.
	(bbdb-mode): Update docstring.

